'''布萊德·菲茲派翠克'''（{{lang-en|Brad Fitzpatrick}}，{{lang-en|Bradley Joseph "Brad" Fitzpatrick}}，{{bd|1980年|2月5日|catIdx=Fitzpatrick, Brad}}），美國知名[[程序员|程序员]]。他最被為人所知的是創辦[[LiveJournal|LiveJournal]]、許多[[自由软件|自由软件]]的開發（如：[[memcached|memcached]]），以及[[OpenID|OpenID]]協定的制定。

== 人物 ==
布萊德出生於[[美國|美國]][[艾奥瓦州|艾奥瓦州]]，並於[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]][[比弗頓|比弗頓]]成長。之後於[[西雅圖|西雅圖]]的[[華盛頓大學_(西雅圖)|華盛頓大學]]就讀[[计算机科学|计算机科学]]。

== 工作 ==
[[LiveJournal|LiveJournal]]後來成為他的全職工作，並且為此成立了一家公司「[[Danga_Interactive|Danga Interactive]]」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.danga.com/faq.bml |title=Danga FAQ |accessdate=2010-11-22 |archive-date=2010-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101121083952/http://danga.com/faq.bml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[2005年1月|2005年1月]]，布萊德以未公開的價錢與股票將LiveJournal賣給[[Six_Apart|Six Apart]]<ref>[http://www.eweek.com/article2/0,1759,1748489,00.asp Six Apart to Buy LiveJournal]</ref>，並成為Six Apart的首席架構師（Chief Architect）<ref>[http://news.livejournal.com/82926.html Big news... Six Apart and LiveJournal!] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100530150815/http://news.livejournal.com/82926.html |date=2010-05-30 }} (5 January 2006)</ref>。

[[2007年8月|2007年8月]]，他離開Six Apart<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mashable.com/2008/02/28/livejournal-advisory-board/ |title=LiveJournal’s New Advisory Board Includes Fitzpatrick |accessdate=2010-11-22 |archive-date=2011-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110127143416/http://mashable.com/2008/02/28/livejournal-advisory-board/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>後就職於[[Google|Google]]<ref>[http://internetcommunications.tmcnet.com/topics/broadband-mobile/articles/19931-google-launches-application-programming-interface-api.htm Google Launches Application Programming Interface (API)] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081104092324/http://internetcommunications.tmcnet.com/topics/broadband-mobile/articles/19931-google-launches-application-programming-interface-api.htm |date=2008-11-04 }}</ref><ref>[http://valleywag.com/tech/brad-fitzpatrick/livejournal-creator-leaves-as-six-apart-fails-to-spin-286218.php LiveJournal creator leaves as Six Apart fails to spin] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071013043244/http://valleywag.com/tech/brad-fitzpatrick/livejournal-creator-leaves-as-six-apart-fails-to-spin-286218.php |date=2007-10-13 }}</ref>，參與[[Android|Android]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://android-developers.blogspot.com/2010/12/new-gingerbread-api-strictmode.html |title=New Gingerbread API: StrictMode |accessdate=2011-09-22 |archive-date=2011-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005231952/http://android-developers.blogspot.com/2010/12/new-gingerbread-api-strictmode.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[PubSubHubbub|PubSubHubbub]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://code.google.com/p/pubsubhubbub/ |title=pubsubhubbub - A simple, open, web-hook-based pubsub protocol & open source reference implementation. - Google Project Hosting |accessdate=2011-09-22 |archive-date=2011-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110923163030/http://code.google.com/p/pubsubhubbub/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及[[Go|Go]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://golang.org/CONTRIBUTORS |title=Text file CONTRIBUTORS - The Go Programming Language |accessdate=2011-09-22 |archive-date=2011-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111009134222/http://golang.org/CONTRIBUTORS |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，並於[[2020年|2020年]][[1月28日|1月28日]]離開[[Google|Google]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://bradfitz.com/2020/01/27/leaving-google |title=An update on bradfitz: Leaving Google |accessdate=2020-01-30 |date=2020-01-27 |language=en |archive-date=2020-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128143625/https://bradfitz.com/2020/01/27/leaving-google |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後加入[[Tailscale|Tailscale]]<ref name="blog20200130"/>。

